# ── Customer PWA configuration ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The ONLY variable this app needs: where the RASA backend lives.
# The Razorpay PUBLIC key is fetched from the backend at runtime (GET /payments/config),
# so NO payment key is ever set here. To turn on live payments you edit only the BACKEND .env
# (PAYMENT_PROVIDER=razorpay + the three RAZORPAY_* keys). See PAYMENTS.md.
VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:3000/api/v1
